    "content": {
        "rendered": "<h2>Basic Setup</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Create a new Field Group</li>\n<li>Add a Gallery field</li>\n<li>Configure options:\n<ul>\n<li>Set image restrictions</li>\n<li>Choose preview size</li>\n<li>Configure min/max images</li>\n<li>Set insert position</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2>Common Use Cases</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Image Collections\n<ul>\n<li>Photo galleries</li>\n<li>Product images</li>\n<li>Portfolio displays</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Media Management\n<ul>\n<li>Slideshows</li>\n<li>Image grids</li>\n<li>Media libraries</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2>Tips</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Set appropriate image limits</li>\n<li>Consider thumbnail sizes</li>\n<li>Enable easy reordering</li>\n<li>Optimize image sizes</li>\n</ul>\n",
